{"tid":822215,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局宣布明日所有學校停課","createTime":"2018-09-16T08:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T09:18:41.000Z","uid":30966,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"83e445f327910744e374b98ab04ed9e57341436b","tid":822215,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"強颱風「山竹」襲港，教育局指，考慮到社區各項設施需時清理和維修，為確保學生安全，教育局宣布明日（17日）無論是否仍有熱帶氣旋警告信號及暴雨警告信號發出，所有學校均停課。<br />\n學校應根據既定的緊急應變措施指引，在安全情況下保持校舍開放，並安排人手在校內安全的地方照顧有確切需要回校的學生，家長應考慮家居、附近的道路、區內天氣、學生的照顧等因素決定是否送子女會回校。"},{"pid":"b861d770dcfc9d999afa2ffeccdc781de116b2c5","tid":822215,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"澳門？"},{"pid":"caa77c8028b8e58191ee3baa6723b7a3537e9de8","tid":822215,"uid":30966,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b861d770dcfc9d999afa2ffeccdc781de116b2c5","tid":822215,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"澳門？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"香港呀"},{"pid":"d5132b78ad6fbf3eedb6f4472af10ba470cf3dcb","tid":822215,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"教育局宣佈明日所有中小學校停課"},{"pid":"c08ad81f9ce6026e7e064fa5c26237fe68e72c20","tid":822215,"uid":91664,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b861d770dcfc9d999afa2ffeccdc781de116b2c5","tid":822215,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"澳門？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"文盲？"},{"pid":"0418ec57e8a407d52179d7f7cca64ae90b3b20f8","tid":822215,"uid":124252,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"U?"},{"pid":"b22494dbe00eb68be07b09de7a849289a84490cf","tid":822215,"uid":404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"太多冧樹 走唔甩停聽日架啦"},{"pid":"4d8e18c407d8283c5f40862cfc04ad8bc807